output: The weather in Carsoli, Italy, over the next five days will feature mostly clear skies with occasional cloud cover. Monday will start with a mix of few and overcast clouds, with temperatures ranging from 3.37°C to 6.42°C and light winds. Tuesday and Wednesday will see predominantly clear skies, with daytime highs reaching 10.14°C and 12.01°C, respectively, and calm winds. Thursday will continue the trend of clear skies, with temperatures peaking at 11.68°C during the day. By Friday, cloud cover will increase slightly, with scattered and broken clouds expected, and temperatures reaching up to 10.93°C. Winds throughout the week will remain light, with no significant gusts.
